*tovid-0.31-r1 (20 Dec 2008)

  20 Dec 2008; <ssuominen@gentoo.org> +files/tovid-0.31-sox.patch,
  +tovid-0.31-r1.ebuild:
  Backported patch from tovid subversion to support new sox wrt #251706,
  thanks to Salah Coronya. Because we have this version of sox in stable,
  and the fix is trivial push it straight to stable for amd64/x86.

